{"tid":171824,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]「梁天恆」終於出世","createTime":"2017-03-25T14:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T16:11:05.000Z","uid":90577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aff6345fa40032732356081c1c5977c1cbedf306","tid":171824,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T14:21:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170325/56478151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170325%2F56478151&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2c2d0f23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170325%2F56478151&h=5b3305f4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170325/56478151</a><br />\n生命影響生命，剛榮升做老竇蘇永康(蘇康)，老婆馮翠珊(Anita)為佢生咗個「慈姑椗」Jazz，係蘇家第一個孫，因為呢個小生命，全家都充滿歡欣。蘇康接受周刊專訪時，講到喺老婆臨入院時，就好情深咁同老婆講，話自己嘅人生係因為佢而改變。<br />\n<br />\n講到改變，蘇康喺專訪到係咁講嘅，活咗49年，由從來沒有想過結婚，就因為現任太太Anita而改變，結咗婚就講明唔生仔，但最後佢都做咗老竇，所以蘇康好情深咁同老婆講係佢改變咗佢，做咗啲佢一直唔想做嘅事，而Anita就回咗蘇康一句話，如果佢冇呢個能力，點去坐呢個位呀！呢啲不經意嘅對答，好不容易令人會feel到佢哋有幾sweet。<br />\n<br />\n天下冇不是之父母，蘇康就同囝囝Jazz講，一定會好好教導佢。蘇康話佢希望囝囝會係一個守法，唔搞事嘅小朋友，但蘇康覺得呢個世代要求小朋友唔搞事都唔容易。蘇康話自己對囝囝嘅要求就一定要識分長幼，即係要對長輩有禮貌，佢仲以霆鋒做例子，話霆鋒雖然好反叛，但佢見到長輩就會立正，九十度鞠躬，所以蘇康唔排除囝囝長大後都會反叛，但佢會悉心咁去教導囝囝，承諾呢個家就係佢嘅後盾。<br />\n<br />\n蘇康又提到，自己喺娛樂圈多年，明白到人情冷暖，有人見高拜見低踩，但佢喺低谷時，就得到媽媽嘅支持，等佢可以繼續行落去，所以佢都會用呢種態度對待自己嘅仔。佢又提到o依家啲人都比較激進，可以話係幾離譜o添，如果好似佢咁，十幾年前犯錯，到o依家都會有人提起，但冇問題㗎，返到屋企父母就要講番正確嘅路應該點行，要聽人家嘅意見同埋好介意別人嘅說話，蘇康話呢個係一個長嘅過程，所以一定要慢慢去教。"},{"pid":"ececb624300ed4a2229627afc3a6b1c3768907cb","tid":171824,"uid":27935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T14:27:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65ae890f3f8ae7e456003bf87a001f9e21cb49fc","tid":171824,"uid":3658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T14:38:09.000Z","msg":"有冇屎忽架"},{"pid":"3a757cb7f42a6af007a84a87147db6064ca0f9c1","tid":171824,"uid":33278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"老豆吸毒對下一代有冇影響"},{"pid":"0b4e78cb8263ec001996636d55e818dea9b7f4d5","tid":171824,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"入嚟之前就諗緊係咪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5879f4a2361907489b04b33383d7f2f8c4e5a4bf","tid":171824,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T15:28:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入嚟之前就諗緊係咪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未出世已經有個咁既花名算唔算慘?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07dd308979eb6e621d783105659cea0ca05f26f3","tid":171824,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T15:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161127/photo/bkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001_01p.jpg?20161127235309\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161127%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20161127235309&h=ac3b8b64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71c23a3b1ffebee5b8d7adf62aa1daea7960734b","tid":171824,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T15:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161127/photo/bkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001_01p.jpg?20161127235309\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161127%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20161127235309&h=ac3b8b64&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4dd07ef24729c931682e793b9111783cd4fc40","tid":171824,"uid":84548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T15:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbc1341100b5b713c8907